Class InitialiseExport

    public abstract class InitialiseExport
extends AbstractOperation<Object,Object>
    A UpdateExport allows the results of a previous operation in an OperationChain to be added to an export, keyed on an optional key. If a key is not provided the default key is 'ALL'.
    See Also:
    UpdateExport, FetchExport, FetchExporter, FetchExporters
